---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Dev Rel Con 2018 — Martyn Davies">
  <main>
    <h1>Dev Rel Con 2018</h1>
    <hr />
    <h2><em>Design Your Content Strategy With Data</em></h2>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="text">
        <p>
          Thanks for checking out the talk! I hope you found it useful and that
          there were some takeaways you can immediately put into place as part of
          your own strategy.
        </p>
        <p>
          The talk was initially longer than the 20 minutes I had on stage so I
          thought I would take a section and offer it up as bonus content if
          people wanted to read it.
        </p>
        <p>
          If one of those people is you then you can download it by clicking on
          the image on the right!
        </p>
        <p class="attribution">
          Download file by ✦ Shmidt Sergey ✦ from the Noun Project
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="download">
        <a
          href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/5m4xkgu3xp9uhbz/Design%20Your%20Content%20Strategy%20with%20Data%20-%20Bonus%20Content.pdf?dl=0"
        >
          <img src="/download.png" width="200" alt="Download bonus content PDF" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .attribution {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #94a3b8;
  }

  .download {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .download img {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
